    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Replacements of one governing administration by another. In later usage, often used as a euphemism for the removal of an illegitimate or hostile government by military force.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
